---Unit weapon state
---
---[<a href="https://github.com/beyond-all-reason/RecoilEngine/blob/56b4f6fef718eede702aff047a043033e011e216/rts/Lua/LuaSyncedRead.cpp#L5107-L5111" target="_blank">source</a>]
